Quietly, without any sound, the amazon assassin crept over to them, watching carefully. She could not see any of them properly, which annoyed the amazon beyond reason.<br>
She suddenly leapt out into their path, sword drawn and in a defensive position.<br>
<br>
“Welcome to the Crimson Valley.” She paused for a moment, “My name is Kalasin Ti’Ya-Kuk’Tai. Can I be of any service to y’all?”<br>
